          "Spanish has two ways to make passives:",
          "",
          "1. SER + PARTICIPLE (formal):        Press 1",
          "El libro fue escrito por Cervantes.",
          "(The book was written by Cervantes.)",
          "La ley será aprobada mañana.",
          "(The law will be approved tomorrow.)",
          "",
