          "(Spanish is spoken here.)",
          "Se venden coches usados.",
          "(Used cars are sold.)",
          "Se construyó el puente en un año.",
          "(The bridge was built in a year.)",
          "",
          "The SE form is much more common in",
          "everyday Spanish."
